{"tid":976150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發有片」全裸大媽進擊大圍中學 學生驚慄尖叫","createTime":"2019-01-10T07:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T10:40:39.000Z","uid":3783,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae08aeec31c58c1a80815155b787519b822aa4f","tid":976150,"uid":3783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190110&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59126902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190110%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59126902&d=pNUid%2BJj0gUX5Bi3f5gA826kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=e89daac3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190110%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59126902&h=5d1242fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190110&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59126902</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朋友之間輸賭，間中都會吹到波咁大話「輸咗我裸跑」，但現實又有幾多人會找數？不過呢，大圍呢位大媽，就真係唔知玩咩玩到咁大，竟然當街裸跑，嚇到途人O晒嘴，噴晒飯！<br />\n<br />\n讀者劉先生今日下晝近1點，喺大圍見到咁驚心動魄嘅呢一幕，當時佢由積泰里一幢大廈，見到一位光脫脫嘅大媽，同警員對峙，其間不停向住附近一間中學大叫，片段見到，一男一女警員雙手捉住大媽，但大媽依然周身郁，最終警員一下反手將佢按落地，另一位就好貼心咁幫佢冚上毛氈遮住，之後又尷尬地行開。過咗冇耐，有一男一女便裝警員趕到，最後大媽由救護車送院。劉先生話當時咁啱係中學午飯時間，一班學生見到即刻尖叫，更加有人歡呼。"},{"pid":"df77a656f57dc6b42e160e422afa4e70dc525c3c","tid":976150,"uid":12458,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:00:52.000Z","msg":"見到要洗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7186683117561c584df6c4feb9efdb19ad56d44","tid":976150,"uid":3783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQ69oBS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQ69oBS.png&h=a96eb3bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1300a85683b60d166466c0a2b86f302faa1a3a99","tid":976150,"uid":17765,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"df77a656f57dc6b42e160e422afa4e70dc525c3c","tid":976150,"uid":12458,"lik